    {
        "content": "<p>Hi there!<br>\nI've been working lately with the sk_buff and I've a few questions about the problems that I've faced. I'd be grateful for help.<br>\nSo, the first one is about the bindgen and <code>__KERNEL__</code> compilation flag (I may be wrong with naming) and the difference in headers :  a lot of the needed functionality which I've used in my C module is under the <code>#ifdef __KERNEL__</code> and some functions are just not available (like <code>ip_hdr</code> fucntion is not available in include header ip.h, but it is available in kernel source ip.h header). Because of this, bindgen can't access ip_hdr function. Firstly, I thought that I will be able to copy the behavior with just by using <code>skb_network_header</code> function as it's done in the kernel sources:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"C\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">static</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kr\">inline</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">iphdr</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">ip_hdr</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">const</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">sk_buff</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">skb</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">iphdr</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"n\">skb_network_header</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">skb</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>But I can't do this, since skb_network_header is not available due to compilation flag.<br>\nOk, this is the function I can just copy it as well. </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"C\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">static</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kr\">inline</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">unsigned</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">char</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"nf\">skb_network_header</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">const</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">sk_buff</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">skb</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">skb</span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"n\">head</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">skb</span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"n\">network_header</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Oops, I can't due to the second issue: bindgen generated rather opaque bindings and there is a duplication of the <code>network_header</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"cp\">#[repr(C)]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">sk_buff</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">__bindgen_anon_1</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">sk_buff__bindgen_ty_1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sk</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sock</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">__bindgen_anon_2</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">sk_buff__bindgen_ty_2</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">cb</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">core</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ffi</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">c_char</span><span class=\"p\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">48</span><span class=\"k\">usize</span><span class=\"p\">],</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">__bindgen_anon_3</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">sk_buff__bindgen_ty_3</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">len</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">core</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ffi</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">c_uint</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">data_len</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">core</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ffi</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">c_uint</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mac_len</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">__u16</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hdr_len</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">__u16</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">queue_mapping</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">__u16</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">__cloned_offset</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">__IncompleteArrayField</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">__u8</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">_bitfield_align_1</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">u8</span><span class=\"p\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">],</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">_bitfield_1</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">__BindgenBitfieldUnit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">u8</span><span class=\"p\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"k\">usize</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">active_extensions</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">__u8</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">__bindgen_anon_4</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">sk_buff__bindgen_ty_4</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">tail</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">sk_buff_data_t</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">end</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">sk_buff_data_t</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">head</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">core</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ffi</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">c_uchar</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">data</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">core</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ffi</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">c_uchar</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">truesize</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">core</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ffi</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">c_uint</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">users</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span 